PRESIDENT OF CZECH REPUBLIC VACLAV HAVEL HOLDS PRESS CONFERENCE AT LES OISEAUX, MARINA MANDARIN HOTEL

Czech President Vaclav Havel and his wife, Mrs Olga Havlova, who are in Singapore for a two-day visit, at press conference held at Les Oiseaux, Marina Mandarin Hotel
